Razmišljao sam da odem.

4
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:22,669
Venecija me cini lenjim.

5
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:26,350
Za to Venecija i postoji.

6
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:28,829
Šta misliš o caši Rosolia?

7
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:32,399
Rosolija?

8
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:35,069
Nisam znao da ga još ima.

9
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:38,755
Kazi mi, kada si došla
u Veneciju?

10
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:42,749
Došla sam ovde 1300-te
sa Kabalistom Mancello Giudeo.

11
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,831
Ah, da...

12
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:48,669
...tada smo bili drugovi
sa Danteom.

13
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:51,310
Trebao bi samo da
otvoriš vrata..

14
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:53,550
da bi se vratio kroz vreme...

15
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:56,430
...baš kao u bajci.

16
00:00:57,880 --> 00:01:00,269
Bilo bi lepo živeti
u bajci.

17
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:04,675
Toj život i jeste kao u bajci,
samo što ti to ne primecuješ.

18
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:07,555
Kad jednom odrastao zakoraci
u svet bajki,

19
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:09,790
nikada ga nemože
napustiti.

20
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,632
Jesili znao za to?

21
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,592
Verovatno smo vec
zakasnili.

22
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,955
Danas je  December, 34-ti.

23
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,555
i još nije Nova godina.

24
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,870
Tako je...

25
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,870
Ali je Božic bio 27-og.

26
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:29,077
Godine u Veneciji uvek
traju duže.

27
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,551
"Prvo ih naciniš lopovima,

28
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:34,280
a onda ih kazniš."

29
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,510
Nikada nisam uspeo da
završim tu knjigu.

30
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:40,838
Ne brini, Corto,
nemožeš žaliti vreme.

31
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,958
Horoskop ti predvidja,dugo
avanturistiško putovanje te ceka.

32
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:47,274
Zaista...

33
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,432
Spavaš...

34
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,073
HONG KONG - February 15, 1919

35
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:04,038
Transformacijom 9-ka postaje...

36
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,839
...postaje živa linija.

37
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:10,596
Jaka linija se može pretvoriti
u malu liniju...

38
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,798
...i dobijamo...

39
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,910
Nemogu da se setim.

40
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,151
Starim.

41
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:23,879
Oh, da! Znak Nubil Devojke.

42
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,190
Nubil Devojka kaže:

43
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,794
"Novi cin heroizma donosi
nesrecu.

44
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,272
Hey, Corto Maltese! Jel' spavaš?

45
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:35,399
Ne... Razmišljam o Veneciji i
o Ear Mouth.

46
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:40,113
Kažeš da devojke nece da se udaju
za avanturiste? - Bezveze...

47
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:42,829
To znaci da se nikada
necu oženiti.

48
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:45,799
Ti od svega praviš šalu, Corto.

49
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,190
Ali ja se nešalim.

50
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,431
Živimo u opasnim vremenima.

51
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:53,717
Rusi se bore na severu,
Japanci na istoku.

52
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:57,236
Sekte postaju politicke
stranke.

53
00:02:57,400 --> 00:03:00,358
Ujedinjuju se protiv stranaca.
Beli Lotos sa...

54
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,272
A šta ti radiš , Long Life?

55
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:05,796
Crveni Trouglovi ocekuju
poruke od Crnih Dijamanata

56
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,951
da ih daju Ružicastim kockama,

57
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,951
koji ce informisati
Bele Trouglove...

58
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,236
Zvuci kao cas iz
geometrije.

59
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:15,312
Corto, Corto...

60
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:17,550
...kad ceš se uozbiljiti?

61
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,631
Ali vec jesam, Long Life.

62
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,910
Na šta ti ja licim?
- Sjajno!

63
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:26,675
Svidja ceš se devojkama
iz Hong Konga.

64
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:30,108
"Ponocni Brat" pozdravlja i
zahvaljuje ti.

65
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:33,238
Triada ce paziti na tebe,
Corto Maltese.

66
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,438
Rat u Evropi je gotov!
nastavlja se u Siberiji,

67
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,670
Mongolia, Manchuria...

68
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,313
Gotov rat u Evropi!

69
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:14,076
Dobro vece, Rasputin.

70
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,112
Šta tražiš u Hong Kong-u?

71
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:19,397
Koliko ja znam Hong Kong nije,
samo za tebe rezervisan.

72
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,870
U tom kišnom kaputu izgledaš
elegantniji..

73
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,473
Poklon.

74
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,232
Svidja ti se?
- Ko?

75
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:26,992
Ova krntija tamo...

76
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:36,754
Jel' ti dosadno?
- Nikada se ne dosadjujem, ti to znaš.

77
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:45,475
Hajdemo, idemo negde na pice.

78
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:50,278
Još uvek živiš u snovima, vidim.

79
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:52,192
Verovatno si u pravu.

80
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,750
Znaš, savšen je trenutak
za biznis.

81
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:57,559
Sa svim tim ratovima izmedju
Boljsevika, i Belih Rusa,

82
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:00,473
Mongoli, Kinezi... postoji nacin
da se covek obogati.

83
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:05,117
To je za lešinare, Ras.

84
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,755
Mogao bih da te ubijem.

85
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,270
Ubi me neki drugi put.

86
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,592
To je krv na tvojem prstu, mornaru!

87
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,955
Gde je covek koji je bio sa tobom?
Gde si krenuo?

88
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:35,076
Jel' to neka
zagonetka?

89
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,870
Trenutna situacija je daleko od
jednostavne,

90
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,270
cak je sasvim zbinjujuca.

91
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,628
Ceo grad je poplavljen
sa Ruskim izbeglicama...

92
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:56,269
...avanturisti... pirati...

93
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:00,519
...kao i osoba koja je
bila sa tobom...

94
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:03,069
...taj Kapetan Rasputin.

95
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,595
Pokušamo mesecima da ga
nadjemo.

96
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,998
Danas smo ga konacno videli...
u tvom društvu!

97
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,878
Sudbina ili slucajnost?

98
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,879
Verovatno i jedno i drugo,
porucnice  Barrow.

99
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,998
Znam dosta stvari o tebi,
Corto Maltese.

100
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:22,118
Bio si u Kini in 1905,
in 1913...

101
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,748
Bili ste gusar
u Južnim Morima.

102
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,559
Cak ste se pridružili tajnom
Kineskom udruženju.

103
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:30,633
Nisam znao da sam ovde toliko
popularan medju policijom.

104
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:34,871
Policajac mora da sumnja u svakoga,
komandantu Maltese.

105
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,951
Mogu li sada da idem?

106
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,589
"Prvo ih naciniš lopovima

107
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,910
a onda ih kazniš."

108
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,230
Nikada nisam uspeo da završim
tu knjigu.

109
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:58,998
Konacno si se vratio, to je divno.

110
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,509
Drago mi je da si ovde.

111
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,992
Takodje, Hu.

112
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,274
Jesili dobila sve što sam ti poslao?
- Da, Corto.

113
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:15,149
Nije sve u novcu. Moramo se videti
s' vremena na vreme...

114
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,838
Jutros je stiglo pismo za tebe.

115
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:23,709
Parfemisano je...

116
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:37,713
"Seti se jutra ispunjenog leptirima
i podnevima ispunjenim divljim cvetovima?"

117
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:40,110
Crveni Fenjeri te ocekuju.

118
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,988
KO su oni? Još jedno
tajno društvo?

119
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:46,757
Crveni Fenjeri su vrlo
hrabre devojke.

120
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,514
Oni su protiv svih ostalih
tajnih društava.

121
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:52,758
Da sam na tvom mestu,
poslušala bi ih.

122
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,714
Rasputin!

123
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,110
Šta sada, Ras? Izgubio si se?

124
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:00,191
Nekada si bio odlican
bacac noževa.

125
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,590
I još uvek sam.

126
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:05,399
U protivnom nbi bio ovde,
bio bi mrtav.

127
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,470
Zašto si nestao popodne?

128
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,233
Iznenadio si se?

129
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:14,551
A ttagovi krvi?
- Hteo sam da se našaliom sa tobom.

130
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,915
Posekao sam se dok si pricao...

131
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:20,038
...da bi poverovao da mi se nešto
loše desilo.

132
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:27,879
Nismo bili u avanturama dugo

133
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:31,077
kao u onoj sa sa Princezom Srece,

134
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:34,596
ostrva Escondida i Santo...
Secaš li se?

135
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:38,594
Ras, t si lud!
- Mogao bih te ubiti.

136
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:41,149
Zar ti ne dosadi da se
stalno ponavljaš?

137
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:58,190
Evo, uzmi tvoj nož.

138
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,078
To nije moj nož!

139
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:05,074
Zar ovo nije nož od tvog
prijatelja?

140
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,832
Da, To je moj nož!

141
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:14,072
Neko je pokušao da te ubije?!

142
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:23,273
Crveni Fenjeri te pozdravljaju,
Corto Maltese.

143
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:27,398
Creveni fenjeri imaju
predlog za tebel.

144
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:29,790
Hoceš li da nas saslušaš?

145
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,918
Spasla si mi život, tako da...

146
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:39,070
Jesili ikada cuo za admiral Kolchak-ov
voz u Siberia?

147
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,595
Voz pun zlata... carevo zlato!

148
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:44,758
Prošle godine, posle pogubljenja
Nikolaja II

149
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:47,718
admiral Kolchak uzeo
kraljevsko blago

150
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:50,678
u ime kontarevolucionarne vlade.

151
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:53,229
Prenosi ga u svom oklopnom vozu.

152
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:57,635
Do sada noko nije uspeo da
presretne voz.

153
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:01,388
Diktatori su vrlo zainteresovani
za kraljevsko blago,

154
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,471
Mandžurijanski banditi,
saveznicke snage i Sibiru

155
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:06,791
i tajna društva...
- Ukljucujuci i vaše?

156
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:11,716
Mi cemo finansirati poduhvat
i obezbediti ljudstvo.

157
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:15,236
Ali nam je potreban neko da
vodi ekspediiju.

158
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:17,914
Mislili smo na tebe,
Corto Maltese.

159
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,275
Dali znaš da je i na u
Hong Kongu?

160
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,158
Ko?

161
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,676
Znaš ti vrlo dobro.

162
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,630
Ona je ovde, ali
neznamo gde.

163
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,916
Ako hoceš, možemo joj
uci u trag.

164
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,708
Možemo iskoristiti te glupe
Crvene Fenjere

165
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:53,871
i uzmemo zlato za nas.

166
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,350
Primam te za partnera.

167
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:59,478
Jesil li završio?
Ako mi prihvatimo...

168
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:03,793
Ako prihvatimo, sve južnije od Moskve
ce biti protiv nas.

169
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,911
Misliš da nam možeš
nabaviti brod?

170
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,230
Napokon! Znao sam!

171
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:20,039
To je Corto kogaja nam!
Corto...

172
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:22,031
...od ranije!

173
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:28,919
Ovo su instrukcije za
Crvene Fenjere iz Šangaja

174
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:31,958
koj ce vam pomoci da dodjete
do Karbina u Mandžuriji.

175
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:36,113
Ova kverta sadrži 1000 funti u zlatu
za pocetne troškove.

176
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,230
Samo cu uzeti uputstva.

177
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:43,476
Ako akcija uspe, podelicemo profit
a i troškove.

178
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:48,031
Ja sam vaš kolega, a ne vaš radnik.
Jelc smo to razjasnili?

179
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,673
Kako želite.

180
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:54,389
Zar niste rekli da je i jedan
saradnik previše?

181
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:58,518
Rekao sam da nevolim paran broj
saradnika.

182
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:00,911
Jedan nije dovoljan

183
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:03,230
tri je previše.

184
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,070
Moramo ici.

185
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,948
Poslacemo nekogaza leš.

186
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,990
Oe je možda još uvek ovde.

187
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:57,790
Možda te ocekuje.

188
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,951
To je stara prica...

189
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:02,839
...ona koju treba zaboraviti.

190
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:05,877
Možda ovo neznaš, ali i ja sam isto
bio nekada zaljubljen.

191
00:17:07,080 --> 00:17:09,310
Devojka iz Nikolajevskog

192
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:12,440
koja je me je cuvala
kad sam bio mali.

193
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:16,110
Majku nikada nisam
poznavao.

194
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:21,069
Umrla je onog dana kad
sam se rodio.

195
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:24,760
Verovatno se uplašila kad
te je videla!

196
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:28,029
Još jedna rec o mojoj majci
i ubicu te.

197
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:31,397
Smiri se, Ras.
Nemam ništa protiv tvoje majke,

198
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,790
osim njee odgovoornosti...

199
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:39,395
Ali tvoj brod je fantastican,
kapetane Rasputin!

200
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:41,551
istina je, imao sam srece.

201
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:44,075
Dobio sam je skoro džabe.

202
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,470
Tvoj prijatelj je takodje
imao srece.

203
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:53,040
Kao to misliš?
- Posada je na platnom spisku

204
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:56,033
Crvenog zalaska sunca.

205
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:59,838
Moraju da te eliminišu pre nego
stignete u Shanghai.

206
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,992
Crveni Zalazak sunca?

207
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:04,151
Tajno društvo.

208
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:07,518
Njihova tradicija im dozvoljava da su
aktivni samo par sati pre zalaska.

209
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:11,358
Crveno simbolizuje krv.
- Fine, te neke tradicije...

210
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:13,750
Instalirali su mitraljez
u potpalublju.

211
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:16,959
Odlazi sada, posmatraju nas.

212
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:37,349
Zar nisi tražio avanturu?
- Šta?

213
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,432
Posada...

214
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:43,992
Pusticu te da središ kapetana.

215
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,359
Ras, gde si?!

216
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,989
Corto Maltese! Ja cu
se pobrinuti za mitraljz...

217
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,956
Hey, ti!

218
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:34,076
Jesili ti bio na tom brodu?
- Jesili jedini preživelir?

219
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:37,516
Izgleda... Ali možeš li
spustiti oružije?

220
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:41,675
Ideš za Shanghai! General Tchang
ce odluciti o tvojoj sudbini!

221
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:14,156
Hajde, mornaru, general Tchang
hoce da razgovara sa tobom.

222
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:24,868
Šta si radio na tom brodu?

223
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:27,909
Jesi li planirao da
se odmetneš u crnoj magiji?

224
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:33,518
Mnoge incidente pripisuju
našim brodovima.

225
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:37,514
Ili nisi imao više para
za bolji brod?

226
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:43,110
Znaš li da imamo zajedniške
prijatelje u Šangaju?

227
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:46,310
Iznenadili ste me, generale.

228
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:49,278
Gospodin Song, milioner.

229
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:51,558
Gospodin Song...

230
00:22:51,760 --> 00:22:54,228
Ili bi trebao reci,
njegovu cerku...

231
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:56,710
...gospodjicu Wee-Lee Song?

232
00:22:57,120 --> 00:23:00,954
Stalno pricaju o tebi u Songovoj kuci,
kamandiru Maltese.

233
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:05,793
Jesi li se vratio u Kinu...
zbog nje?

234
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:08,791
Ne, budite sigurni.

235
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:12,316
Gospodjica Wee-Lee Song nije povezana
sa mojom posetom.

236
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:17,031
Ako nije žena zaslužna za
vaše prisustvo...

237
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:19,760
...moždaje voz.

238
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:22,720
Ruski, na primer...

239
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,871
...pun zlata?

240
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:28,071
Neznam na šta mislite.

241
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,551
Baš cudno...

242
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:36,508
Ovih dana mnogi ljudi umiru
a da neznaju ni zašto.

243
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:47,031
Ah, šaj!

244
00:23:47,520 --> 00:23:49,476
Jedno od retkih zadovoljstava
na ovom svetu.

245
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:52,480
A One Ear pravi jako
dobar caj.

246
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:55,191
Hvala ti, One Ear.

247
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:57,351
One Ear je Tibetanski monah.

248
00:23:57,840 --> 00:24:00,229
Nacuo je nešto što nije smeo..

249
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:02,550
pa su mu odsekli jedno uvo.

250
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:06,190
Ali pravi odlican caj.

251
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:10,954
Ja sam slep, gluv i mutav,
generale...

252
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:13,111
...baš kao i tri monaha.

253
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:21,992
To je bio jedan koji nije
znao pricu o tri monaha.

254
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:25,031
Možete ici, kamandiru Maltese.

255
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:38,354
Zašto ste ga pustili, generale?

256
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:41,759
Zato što ce me on odvesti do
voza punog blaga.

257
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:57,630
Još jedna žrtva ludila!
Još veselja!

258
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:01,755
Dali uvek dolaziš u saunu sa
cigaromi pištoljem?

259
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:06,314
Da. Zato što sam ja Jack Tippit...
Americke Aviacije.

260
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:09,431
A moja cigara nikada
nije zapljena,

261
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,955
ofe fine "Connecticut Cigare"
uvek nestanu.

262
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,713
A šešir?

263
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:17,678
Neznam zapravo.
A ti?

264
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:19,752
Šta ja?

265
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:20,955
Ko si ti?

266
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:23,350
Postavio si mi
previše pitanja .

267
00:26:23,520 --> 00:26:27,672
Ti si Anarhista? Boljšhevik?
Jedan od romantišnih revolucionara?

268
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:30,950
Postavljaš mnoga pitanja.
Ono što ti mogu reci je

269
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:33,350
da dobar ubod nožem uvek ide
od podnožja do vrha.

270
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:36,876
Smiri se, neželim probleme.

271
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:39,873
Umoran sam, vrlo
sam umoran.

272
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:42,232
Onda se odmori.

273
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,152
Ne mogu.

274
00:26:44,320 --> 00:26:48,074
Stalno razmišljam o ženi ,
sa njenim vozom punim Kozaka i ubica.

275
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,595
Ako poznaješ vojvodkinju...

276
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:55,275
Verovatno si primetio da
nebi bilo rata da nema vozova.

277
00:26:57,040 --> 00:27:01,192
Neverovatno! Jedina stvar za koju znaju,
je to sklonište u tom vozu

278
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:04,158
nadajuci se da ce izbeci konflikt,
dok se drugi nadaju da ga kontrolišu.

279
00:27:05,040 --> 00:27:08,237
Sve prevoze u vozovima,
cak i njihovu domovinu!

280
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:10,630
Cak i sveto Rusko blago!

281
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:14,398
Još uvek mi nisi rekao šta
radiš u Šangaju.

282
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:17,830
Samo prolazim.

283
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:20,195
Moram da odem do Kharbina
u Mandžuriji.

284
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:24,875
I ja tu idem. Možemo podeliti mesto,
u mom avionu.

285
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:28,357
Nikada nisi leteo ranije?

286
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:32,158
Ne! I nebi želeo da
pokušavam.

287
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:02,029
Taj šlem ti baš odgovara.
Liciš na moju tetku.

288
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:04,709
Necu ti reci na
šta ti liciš!

289
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:11,112
Samo još dva dana,
ukljucujuci pauze.

290
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:13,032
Zacepi!

291
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:04,149
Prati nas onaj avion.

292
00:29:04,320 --> 00:29:05,958
Što misliš da nas prate?

293
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:27,274
Dosadno mi je, Spatzetov... Mnogo
mi je dosadno.

294
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:32,632
Daj mi novine.

295
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:35,635
Na nesrecu vec su stare
nedelju dana.

296
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:37,711
Nemoguce je naci druge.

297
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:40,119
To je major Tippit.

298
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,992
Tippit?

299
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:44,435
Budi fin i obori ga!

300
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:58,392
Jesili u redu?

301
00:31:02,080 --> 00:31:06,312
Corto, dozvoli mi da ti predstavim jednog
od najvecih kuckinih sinova...

302
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:09,870
...major Spatzetov,
Ussuri kozaka.

303
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:12,711
Zao mi je majore.

304
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:15,030
Mislili smo da je jedan od
onih Boljševika.

305
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:17,590
Kako da vam
nadoknadim gubitak?

306
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:19,831
Nadam se da niste
mnogo uzneiran?

307
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:26,879
Nadajte se cemu ocete, vojvodkinje...
ali US vlada.

308
00:31:27,040 --> 00:31:29,110
može odustati takodje.

309
00:31:29,280 --> 00:31:31,919
Oni baš i nevole kad im
se obori avion.

310
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:37,712
Ova popodneva u Sibiru
izgledaju ka noci.

311
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:44,069
Kako ste, vojvotkinjo?

312
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:47,831
Fino, hvala Bogu.

313
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,355
Mislila sam na tebe, Tippit.

314
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,359
Jel tvoj prijatelj
povredjen?

315
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:59,871
Molim vas ucinite mi uslugu
i držite me podalje od vaših ''poslova''.

316
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:02,549
Tvoj prijatelj ima gadnu
narav, Tippit.

317
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,597
On voli grubu igru.

318
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:06,591
Ali je hrabar momak.

319
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,632
Kako mu je ime?

320
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,119
Corto Maltese.

321
00:32:15,360 --> 00:32:19,433
Vojvotkinja je izrazila zadovoljstvo
da te upozna.

322
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:35,600
Ne verujem u to prijateljstvo sa
saveznickim snagama.

323
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:39,036
Ako im ''naša stvar'' ne donese dobit,
odmah ce nas ostaviti.

324
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:43,591
U pravu si.

325
00:32:43,760 --> 00:32:45,830
Bolje bi bilo biti uz Von Ungern-a

326
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:49,913
i zajedno sa njim i Semenovim organizovati
borbu protiv Boljševika...

327
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:51,752
...i ako je Von Ungern ludak!

328
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:54,790
Da, možda.

329
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:57,430
On zamišlja novu hordu
elitnih ratnika koja ce doci

330
00:32:57,600 --> 00:33:00,068
iz Mongilija.
On sanja o

331
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:03,437
ustolicenju Azijske imperije
da bi porazio Evropu.

332
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:08,153
On je ubedjen da je reinkarnacija
Džingis Kana!

333
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:11,955
To je tako romanticno!

334
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:15,917
Ali istina je mi i nismo tako
dobro organizovani.

335
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:18,790
Na cijoj si strani, Spatzetov?

336
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,791
Vašoj, vaše Velicanstvo.

337
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:23,599
Vi ste najinteresantnija
žena koju sam ikada upoznao!

338
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:48,110
Koliko dugo je poznaješ?

339
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:52,829
Od prošlog leta u Vladivostoku.

340
00:33:53,560 --> 00:33:56,996
Zabava povodom dolaska Americkih trupa
... sve te budalaštine...

341
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:59,230
...uobicajne gluposti...

342
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:02,280
Bili su darežljivi na kavijaru,
šampanjcu...

343
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:04,351
...i vojvotkinji.

344
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:15,078
Želeo bi da izadjem na
Mandžurijskoj granici.

345
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:17,391
Mandžurija je opasna.

346
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:19,073
Moram da odem
do Karbina.

347
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:22,030
Probacu da ti pomognem,
Cortushka...

348
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:23,713
...ali Sibirska granica je

349
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:26,189
pod kontrolom barona
Von Ungern-Sternberga.

350
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,395
Ko je to?

351
00:34:27,560 --> 00:34:30,199
Disident Teutonickih Vitezova.

352
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:32,999
Njegova porodica je bila
likvidirana tokom revolucije.

353
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:36,831
Možeš li...?

354
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,752
Moja ogrlica...

355
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:43,950
Osecam toplinu.

356
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:46,589
Da, i ja sam igrala
i pila nekada sa muškarcima.

357
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:49,228
Nekada se moraš zabaviti.

358
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:51,550
Pogotovo ako si posle u stanju

359
00:34:51,720 --> 00:34:54,359
da tražiš oprost od Našega Gospoda.

360
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:18,508
To je Semenov, vodja
Baikalskih kozaka,

361
00:36:18,680 --> 00:36:21,240
general Brutalne Division...

362
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:25,718
Uglavnom znan po svojoj
reputaciji ubice.

363
00:36:32,120 --> 00:36:35,112
Moja draga Marina, jeste li
dobro putovali?

364
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:37,871
Sergey Semenov, prijatelju moj...

365
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:40,793
...putovanje kroz Manchuria
je dobro prošlo.

366
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:42,996
Kinezi i Japanci te obožavaju.

367
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:46,516
Nevole me,
oni me...

368
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:48,511
Zašto nebi predstavila svoje
prijatelje.

369
00:36:48,680 --> 00:36:53,071
Komandir Corto Maltese i major Tippit
iz Americke avijacije.

370
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,757
Semenov...

371
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:58,036
Koji samo veruje u
oklopne vozove.

372
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:02,759
I ti bi trebala u njih da
veruješ, Marina.

373
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:06,913
Dodji da vidiš šta su mi dali Japanci.
Vi takodje, gospodo.

374
00:37:07,080 --> 00:37:09,878
Siguran sam da ce
vas zanimati.

375
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:15,630
Dozvolite mi da va predstavim mog
"Razaraca".

376
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:19,634
Mogu se odupreti bilo kom
Boljševickom oružiju.

377
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:23,628
Moji vozovi i topovi
su mocni...

378
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:26,110
Teški su, i spori..

379
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:30,754
Zar vam nikada nisu rekli
"u zatvorena usta muva ne ulece".

380
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,991
Corto Maltese...

381
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:36,348
Tvoje ime mi je poznato.

382
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:39,309
Ili možda tvoje lice.

383
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:42,268
Mora da sa te negde video.

384
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:44,271
Nemoguce je.

385
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:49,156
Moje lice nikada nije promenilo mesto.
Uvek je bilo moje!

386
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:52,916
Sergey, ja moram da nastavim
svoje putovanje.

387
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:55,471
Kolchak nece cekati.

388
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:59,155
Istina. a ti si jedina kome
admiral još uvek veruje.

389
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:02,630
Naša sudbina ce uskoro
biti u našim rukama, Marina.

390
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,677
Major Tippit ce putovati sa nama.

391
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:09,072
Corto Maltese mora da stigne do Karbina
u Mandžuriji. Možeš li mi pomoci?

392
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:10,832
Pobrinucu se.

393
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,877
Na koji nacin?

394
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:17,232
Ne brini, Marina, tvom mornaru
se nece ništa desiti.

395
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:32,997
Nadam se da cu te videti...
jednog dana.

396
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:36,472
I ja.
- Ne veruj Semenovu.

397
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:39,630
Vidimo se, Corto.

398
00:38:40,720 --> 00:38:42,517
Vidimo se, Jack.

399
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:14,432
General Semenov mi je naredio da
te ubijem cim predjemo granicu.

400
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:18,031
Corto Maltese...

401
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,118
Dobrodošao u Mandžuriju!

402
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:29,079
Semenovu se nesvodjaš.

403
00:39:30,200 --> 00:39:32,794
I on se meni nesvidja.

404
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:45,516
Dobrodošao, Corto Maltese.

405
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,550
Jesmo li se vec sreli?

406
00:40:54,120 --> 00:40:56,429
Pomogla sam ti na brodu.

407
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:59,071
Imao sam prijatelja na tom brodu.

408
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,755
Prijatelj?

409
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,592
Znaš li nešto o njemu?

410
00:41:03,160 --> 00:41:06,436
Možda. Dodji, ocekuju te.

411
00:41:10,120 --> 00:41:12,270
Došao je trenutak, Corto.

412
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:16,597
Nisam ocekivao da cu naici na Crvene
Fenjere tako daleko na Severu.

413
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:19,399
Interesi nepoznaju granice.

414
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,554
Tacno.

415
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:24,996
Ratovi u Kini i Mandžuriji
uništavaju naš narod.

416
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:28,679
Imamo mnogo toga da
naucimo od Rusa.

417
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,950
U celoj državi imaju struju,

418
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:34,680
još malo pa ce iskoreniti
nepismenost.

419
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:37,957
Dobro, ali ja vam netrebam da bi
edukovali naciju.

420
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:41,230
Gde je taj famozni brod?

421
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:44,110
Jeste li bili u stanju da ga
locirate?

422
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:48,749
Kolchak je naišao na otpor
u Irkutsku.

423
00:41:48,920 --> 00:41:52,833
Ali on hoce da ode , a Semenov
je spreman da ga napadne.

424
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:54,958
Ko to peva?

425
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:58,837
Ruski oficir.
Zove se Nino.

426
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:03,719
Dobrodošao, mornaru !
Hoceš popiti nešto?

427
00:42:03,960 --> 00:42:06,349
Još ne.
- Zašto?

428
00:42:06,520 --> 00:42:08,829
Pre ili kasnije picemo
zajedno.

429
00:42:13,080 --> 00:42:16,072
Sudbina hoce od nas da
volimo istu ženu.

430
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:19,309
Vrlo tešku ženu.

431
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:21,118
Ona mi je ukrala dušu.

432
00:42:22,280 --> 00:42:23,998
Pricaš pricu.

433
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,352
Možda...

434
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:29,239
...prica mi je samo i ostala.

435
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:34,228
Uz ovakav sneg cak i Rusi i
Mandžurijci ostaju u kuci.

436
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:37,311
Kako da te zovem?

437
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:41,073
Zovi me Changaï-Li.

438
00:42:41,240 --> 00:42:42,229
Spreman sam.

439
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:44,834
Zašto nosiš tu paradnu
uniformu?

440
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:48,470
Zato što, moj dragi prijatelju, sam još
uvek deo vojnickog ludila.

441
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:51,312
Secaš se?

442
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:53,471
Ona je volela uniforme.

443
00:42:53,640 --> 00:42:55,710
Ali ko zna kome je još
dala svoju dušu?

444
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:58,155
Nino, nemoj opet da
pocinješ!

445
00:42:59,720 --> 00:43:02,280
Moraš upozoriti
generala Tchang.

446
00:43:06,040 --> 00:43:07,951
Corto, bice ti potrebno
prerušavanje.

447
00:43:08,120 --> 00:43:10,111
Ili ce te Semenov prepoznati.

448
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:13,716
Semenov... Imao bi
šta d mu kažem.

449
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:18,752
Semenov je u isto vreme najgori
prijatelj i najgori neprijatelj koga možeš imati.

450
00:43:19,240 --> 00:43:21,310
Kako si ga upoznao?

451
00:43:21,480 --> 00:43:24,517
Vojvotkinja Marina Seminova
nas je upoznala.

452
00:43:25,480 --> 00:43:27,232
Jel' lepa, vojvotkinja?

453
00:43:27,880 --> 00:43:30,269
Da... Reao bih da jeste.

454
00:43:32,200 --> 00:43:33,952
Šta si rekao?

455
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:36,159
Rekao sam da.

456
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:38,197
Kad si pored nje
kao da si

457
00:43:38,360 --> 00:43:40,351
pored neceg toplog,
necega mekanog...

458
00:43:48,120 --> 00:43:49,599
Srecan Božic, Corto!

459
00:43:54,520 --> 00:43:57,159
Corto, Corto, prijatelju...
Srecan Božic!

460
00:43:57,480 --> 00:43:59,471
Ali danas nije Božic?

461
00:43:59,640 --> 00:44:00,868
Pa šta?

462
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:04,597
Mi, avanturisti, proslavljamo Božic
kad mi to želimo.

463
00:44:04,760 --> 00:44:08,833
Ponovo sam te našao, Corto
lepo je ponoviti tvoje ime...

464
00:44:10,520 --> 00:44:14,035
Rasputin, jesili to
stvarno ti?

465
00:44:14,280 --> 00:44:17,238
Da, nego ko drugi? Tvoja tetka?

466
00:44:18,120 --> 00:44:22,511
Nestao si blizu Šangajai... a sada
te nalazim blizu Sibira.

467
00:44:22,840 --> 00:44:25,070
Uvek si me podcenjivao.

468
00:44:25,240 --> 00:44:27,231
To je tvoja greška.

469
00:44:34,360 --> 00:44:36,271
Kaviar i vodka, Corto!

470
00:44:36,440 --> 00:44:38,112
Jedine stvari iz moje zemlje...

471
00:44:38,520 --> 00:44:40,590
...baš kao i zlato koje ceš ukrasti.

472
00:44:40,760 --> 00:44:42,990
Zlato  Rusije!

473
00:44:45,080 --> 00:44:48,117
To nece biti tako lako,
sa Semenovim...

474
00:44:49,160 --> 00:44:51,720
Bila su dva prijatelja samnom.
Gde su oni?

475
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:55,317
Imaš samo jednog prijatelja, i
to sam ja. Razumeš?

476
00:44:57,200 --> 00:44:59,555
Hajde da se malo pozabavimo
sa tim Semenovim.

477
00:45:07,560 --> 00:45:11,792
Komandante, Amerikanci kontrolišu
prugu blizu Tchita.

478
00:45:11,960 --> 00:45:13,791
Americanci?

479
00:45:16,120 --> 00:45:18,429
Misli sam dasu to Japanci.

480
00:45:18,600 --> 00:45:19,749
Bilo kako bilo...

481
00:45:19,920 --> 00:45:22,309
...ono što je važno za nas,
je raskršce u Karimskom.

482
00:45:22,480 --> 00:45:25,472
Tu ce mo sacekati Kolcakov voz.

483
00:45:27,080 --> 00:45:29,640
Proveri dali je pruga slobodna
za naš povratak.

484
00:45:30,360 --> 00:45:31,952
Razumem, komandiru.

485
00:45:32,440 --> 00:45:34,510
I neuznemiravaj me više!

486
00:45:43,960 --> 00:45:45,473
Zašto me tako gledaš?

487
00:45:45,800 --> 00:45:47,791
I ti mene gledaš!

488
00:45:48,120 --> 00:45:50,554
Hey, vas dvoje! Jel' vi pripadate

489
00:45:50,720 --> 00:45:52,790
nekom pozorištu sa maskama?

490
00:45:53,560 --> 00:45:55,073
Koje maske?

491
00:45:55,240 --> 00:45:57,879
O kom pozorištu pricaš, idiote?

492
00:45:58,120 --> 00:46:01,590
Mi smo oficiri Venetian marinaca,
poslati ka savetnici

493
00:46:01,760 --> 00:46:04,911
za Sibirske i Mongolske kozake.

494
00:46:05,480 --> 00:46:08,597
A zašto ne onda Marko Polo i njegova ž
tetka na putu za Kjoto?

495
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:10,672
Pokažite mi vaše isprave!

496
00:46:10,840 --> 00:46:15,960
Trenutak, captain.Mogu da garantujem
za ova dva oficira. Možete ici.

497
00:46:16,120 --> 00:46:17,792
Razumem!

498
00:46:19,880 --> 00:46:22,599
Nebi ga trebao tako kinjiti.
Nije on imbecil.

499
00:46:22,760 --> 00:46:25,149
Nismo znali da su Kozaci
izgubili smisao za humor.

500
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:29,397
Zbog Semenova, i oni kojima je imalo
ostalo, su ga izgubili.

501
00:46:29,800 --> 00:46:31,438
Šta se to desilo te noci?

502
00:46:31,800 --> 00:46:34,109
Nestao si u toj mecavi.

503
00:46:34,280 --> 00:46:37,158
Uvek se izgubim u mecavama.
Neznam šta da radim.

504
00:46:55,480 --> 00:46:57,471
Jel to vojvodkinja?
- Verujem da jeste.

505
00:46:57,640 --> 00:47:00,598
Još malo.
Konacno smo izašli odavde.

506
00:47:00,760 --> 00:47:02,591
Gde da bi otišao?

507
00:47:34,840 --> 00:47:37,957
Vaše Velicanstvo, Boljševici
su zauzeli Irkutsk.

508
00:47:38,120 --> 00:47:39,633
Naš puk je desetkovan.

509
00:47:39,800 --> 00:47:42,997
pšovukli smo se,
ali više nemožemo da cekamo.

510
00:47:43,240 --> 00:47:44,639
A admiral?

511
00:47:47,400 --> 00:47:51,029
Admiral-baron Kolchak je izdan od strane
Cekoslovackih legionara.

512
00:47:51,200 --> 00:47:54,829
Boljševici su ga ubili
i bacilio njegovo telo u reku Angara.

513
00:47:55,080 --> 00:47:56,991
Moramo otici, vaše Velicanstvo.

514
00:47:57,160 --> 00:47:58,912
Transportovanje zlata bi
previše trajalo.

515
00:47:59,080 --> 00:48:01,230
Zajedno sa vašim
trupama u vozu.

516
00:48:11,080 --> 00:48:14,356
Šast da sacuvate Carsko
blago je vaše.

517
00:48:14,520 --> 00:48:17,080
Njgovo velicanstvo admiral-baron
je želeo ako da bude.

518
00:49:20,120 --> 00:49:23,237
Sergey, kakvi su Amerikanci?

519
00:49:24,680 --> 00:49:27,558
Amerikanci? Oni su Židovi...

520
00:49:27,720 --> 00:49:29,870
...ništa do jevreja sa Wall Street-a.

521
00:49:30,040 --> 00:49:34,989
Ungernje upravu kad kaže da
hoceda uzmu ceo svet.

522
00:49:35,560 --> 00:49:38,438
Ali nisu bankari samo Židovi.

523
00:49:39,560 --> 00:49:43,314
Lenin and Trotsky su židovi takodje...

524
00:49:44,520 --> 00:49:47,637
...subverzivni i boljševicki jevreji...

525
00:49:47,800 --> 00:49:50,519
Moja porodica je takodje
jevrejska, Sergey.

526
00:49:51,560 --> 00:49:54,711
Ja sam ti spasao porodicu.
Jesili to zaboravila?

527
00:49:55,320 --> 00:49:59,552
Ne! Samo sam mislila...

528
00:50:01,400 --> 00:50:03,960
Pocela si da misliš, Masha?!

529
00:50:07,720 --> 00:50:09,870
Generale...
- Neuznemiravaj me, rekao sam!

530
00:50:10,040 --> 00:50:11,712
Dovedi mi drugu devojku.

531
00:50:16,120 --> 00:50:19,157
Kada objekat hoce da postane
subjekat...

532
00:50:19,400 --> 00:50:21,311
...postane beskoristan.

533
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:25,834
Hoceš da ideš istim putem?

534
00:50:27,160 --> 00:50:29,958
Jesilio ti isto slobodomišljenik?

535
00:50:30,440 --> 00:50:34,194
Ja sam tek stigla.
sa jednim odf tvojih oficira...

536
00:50:36,760 --> 00:50:38,034
...kapetan Jaroslav.

537
00:50:39,640 --> 00:50:41,392
Ah, Nino!

538
00:50:42,120 --> 00:50:44,509
Budala koja je izgubila
svoju dušu.

539
00:50:44,680 --> 00:50:46,830
S' vremena na vreme ode
da je potraži

540
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:50,276
a onda se vrati bez uspeha.

541
00:50:50,680 --> 00:50:54,036
Jednog dana cu mu
odrati kožu.

542
00:50:54,280 --> 00:50:56,111
Dodji ovamo.

543
00:51:02,280 --> 00:51:03,554
Spusti se.

544
00:51:03,720 --> 00:51:07,156
Mnogo si otišla daleko na sever
s' obzirom da si iz Shangaja.

545
00:51:07,800 --> 00:51:09,711
Šta tražiš ovde?

546
00:51:10,120 --> 00:51:13,192
Zar neznaš da ceš ovde pre umreti
nego naci nešto?

547
00:51:13,560 --> 00:51:15,676
Tražim zlatnog zmaja.

548
00:51:16,360 --> 00:51:18,590
Zlatnog zmaja?

549
00:51:19,880 --> 00:51:21,996
Mora da si luda.

550
00:51:23,320 --> 00:51:26,039
Ali o znašta swe krije
iza tvog ludila?

551
00:51:26,600 --> 00:51:28,238
Sa mi miluj glavu...

552
00:51:29,640 --> 00:51:31,870
Hocu da spavam.

553
00:51:34,400 --> 00:51:37,073
Takav sam kakav sam
i nemogu više da brinem o politici

554
00:51:37,240 --> 00:51:40,118
zato što sam izabrao
put novca,

555
00:51:40,280 --> 00:51:43,477
prelepih žena i finih stvari.

556
00:51:44,280 --> 00:51:46,271
Zato moram da kradem.

557
00:51:47,080 --> 00:51:49,310
Ali... ti si lopov.

558
00:51:49,960 --> 00:51:52,190
Naravno da sam lopov.

559
00:51:52,600 --> 00:51:55,068
Ali cim nešto ukradem,
odmah ga potrošim.

560
00:51:55,240 --> 00:51:57,310
Tako novac cirkuliše!

561
00:51:57,720 --> 00:52:00,996
Mnogi ljudi žive zahvaljujuci novcu
koji ukradem.

562
00:52:01,160 --> 00:52:04,118
Kolcakov brod!
Dolazi!

563
00:52:05,400 --> 00:52:07,072
Na svoje položaje! Požurite!

564
00:52:07,320 --> 00:52:11,279
Ta mlada devojkal... Changaï-Li...
Gde je ona?

565
00:52:11,880 --> 00:52:14,440
I ona jena ovom brodu.

566
00:52:14,680 --> 00:52:17,558
I spremna za veliki trenutak,
baš kao i mi!

567
00:54:07,720 --> 00:54:10,359
Kad se sve uzme u obzir, ovo je možda
najbolji nacin da se umre,

568
00:54:10,520 --> 00:54:12,750
biti ubijen od svojih...

569
00:55:50,760 --> 00:55:55,197
Taj Semenov je neverovatan momak!
-Koljac, da!

570
00:55:55,480 --> 00:55:57,072
On je završio ceo posao!

571
00:55:57,240 --> 00:56:00,994
Neka neko otkaci vagon sa zlatom!
Brzo!

572
00:56:01,560 --> 00:56:03,278
Polazim, komandiru!

573
00:56:11,400 --> 00:56:12,719
Izdajice!

574
00:56:20,680 --> 00:56:22,671
Htela je da te ubije!

575
00:56:32,680 --> 00:56:34,989
Bolje bi bilo da se skoncentrišemo
na zlato.

576
00:56:35,640 --> 00:56:38,108
I prestani da misliš na žene!

577
00:56:38,280 --> 00:56:40,191
Posle revolucije bicemo bogati

578
00:56:40,360 --> 00:56:43,557
a svet ce biti preplavljen sa
ruskim vojvodkinjama !

579
00:57:39,080 --> 00:57:42,277
Ah ti si, Nino.
Šta se dešava?

580
00:57:42,760 --> 00:57:44,671
Našao si svoju dušu?

581
00:57:45,160 --> 00:57:48,038
Ne Semenov, još uvek
je nisam našao

582
00:57:48,280 --> 00:57:50,430
ali cu te ubiti.

583
00:57:51,640 --> 00:57:53,153
Ne zbog zlata...

584
00:57:53,320 --> 00:57:55,914
...vec zato što si ubica,

585
00:57:56,080 --> 00:57:57,752
nedostojan armije.

586
00:57:59,400 --> 00:58:00,674
Pazi!

587
00:58:36,560 --> 00:58:38,551
Oni imaju crnog zmaja na dlanu.

588
00:58:38,720 --> 00:58:40,517
Mora da su Triade.

589
00:58:41,000 --> 00:58:43,230
Ne, nisu Triade.

590
00:58:43,400 --> 00:58:46,756
Crni Zmaj je sekta kojoj
je on pripadao.

591
00:58:48,760 --> 00:58:50,512
Gde je Semenov otišao?

592
00:58:50,920 --> 00:58:52,751
U lokomotivu.

593
00:59:04,680 --> 00:59:08,434
Lepše bi ti stajalo to krzno od, leoparda
moja mala Changaï-Li.

594
00:59:14,120 --> 00:59:16,839
Nemam više leopardovo krzno...

595
00:59:17,000 --> 00:59:19,070
...ali još uvek imam njegove celjusti!

596
00:59:54,000 --> 00:59:55,797
Brže!

597
01:00:02,120 --> 01:00:03,553
Nerazumem.

598
01:00:03,720 --> 01:00:06,188
Ta cetrdesetpetica mi izgleda
vrlo jasno!

599
01:00:06,920 --> 01:00:10,674
Zlato u vozu ce poslužiti
Azijskoj revoluciji.

600
01:00:11,400 --> 01:00:14,039
Rusija je dugo eksploatisala
moj narod.

601
01:00:14,200 --> 01:00:17,078
Jedino je fer da
Zapadnjaci plate za to.

602
01:00:17,400 --> 01:00:20,597
Ako hoceš da ostaneš živ,
iskoci iz voza.

603
01:00:20,760 --> 01:00:24,435
Devojko, Rusia jer napravila mnogo grešaka,
to je istina.

604
01:00:24,600 --> 01:00:26,079
Ali ja sam Ruski oficir

605
01:00:26,240 --> 01:00:29,073
i zato da moram da branim sve
što pripada Rusiji.

606
01:00:29,240 --> 01:00:32,915
A što se mene tice,
mogu i da poginem.

607
01:00:37,640 --> 01:00:39,471
Devojko?!

608
01:00:44,360 --> 01:00:49,070
Nikada nisam cuo takvo
glupo razmišljanje!

609
01:03:00,280 --> 01:03:02,271
"Na plavim letnjim nocima,

610
01:03:02,440 --> 01:03:04,192
krenucu putem,

611
01:03:04,360 --> 01:03:07,477
opecen listovima kukuruza,
teturajuci se po travi.

612
01:03:08,600 --> 01:03:12,036
U snovima oseticu njnu hladnocu
na mojim stopalima.

613
01:03:12,560 --> 01:03:15,028
Pusticu da vetar šiba
moju golu glavu.

614
01:03:15,720 --> 01:03:18,837
i necu misliti na ništa.

615
01:03:19,400 --> 01:03:22,198
Ali beskrajna ljubav ce
kukati u mojoj duši,

616
01:03:22,360 --> 01:03:25,796
I oticicu daleko, tako daleko,
ka cigan,

617
01:03:27,880 --> 01:03:30,838
Kroz predele - srecan

618
01:03:32,040 --> 01:03:34,031
kao da sam bio sa ženom."

619
01:03:38,840 --> 01:03:40,990
O cemu misliš, Corto?

620
01:03:41,560 --> 01:03:44,438
Arthur Rimbaud, francuski pesnik.

621
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:47,389
U takvim trenutcima nemislim
ninašta drugo.

622
01:04:05,240 --> 01:04:07,549
Vi ste zatvorenici

623
01:04:07,720 --> 01:04:09,597
Baron Von Ungern-Sternberg-ove konjice!

624
01:04:25,640 --> 01:04:27,471
Imaš lepe ruke...

625
01:04:27,640 --> 01:04:29,392
...ali majušne.

626
01:04:31,880 --> 01:04:35,236
Kada si bio dete, mora da si
bio bucmast i debeljuškast.

627
01:04:35,800 --> 01:04:38,439
Ostavi moje ruke na miru
i reci mi šta vidiš.

628
01:04:38,600 --> 01:04:42,479
Tvoj život ce biti kratak, Von Ungern...
vrlo kratak.

629
01:04:42,680 --> 01:04:45,353
Možda još dve godine... ne više.

630
01:04:46,120 --> 01:04:47,997
I mnogo krvi...

631
01:04:48,280 --> 01:04:50,032
Dve godine...

632
01:04:50,440 --> 01:04:52,829
To bi trebalo biti dovoljno da
ispunim zadatak.

633
01:04:53,160 --> 01:04:57,278
Šta još vidiš?
- Samo vidim krv... krv.

634
01:04:57,440 --> 01:04:59,396
Hocu li pobediti?

635
01:04:59,560 --> 01:05:02,313
Sve što vidim je da si mnoge
poubijao...

636
01:05:02,920 --> 01:05:05,309
...i pune kofe krvi!

637
01:05:31,560 --> 01:05:35,235
Našli smo ih u planinama,
blizu jezera Tromedje.

638
01:05:41,720 --> 01:05:44,188
Šta ste radili izmedju Mongolije
i Mandžurije?

639
01:05:44,360 --> 01:05:47,955
Necete mi verovati, ali pokušavam
nekoga da zaboravim.

640
01:05:48,680 --> 01:05:51,797
Izgledaš kao cigan
ili mornar,

641
01:05:52,600 --> 01:05:54,830
nosiš oficirsku kapu.

642
01:05:55,000 --> 01:05:56,991
To je bio poklon.

643
01:05:57,400 --> 01:05:59,630
Pa?
- Pa šta?

644
01:05:59,800 --> 01:06:02,268
Cekam!
- Šta cekaš?

645
01:06:10,760 --> 01:06:13,877
Došli smo u ovu prelepu zemlju
da ukrademo zlato iz voza

646
01:06:14,760 --> 01:06:17,399
koje je i Semenov hteo da
uzme sa sebe.

647
01:06:17,560 --> 01:06:19,790
A kako se prica završava?

648
01:06:20,280 --> 01:06:21,793
Nemam pojima.

649
01:06:21,960 --> 01:06:24,918
Mogu samo da vam kažem
da Semenov nije uspeo.

650
01:06:27,400 --> 01:06:28,753
Dobro!

651
01:06:29,560 --> 01:06:30,913
Dobro!

652
01:06:31,080 --> 01:06:33,719
Uzevši to u obzir,
necu vas pogubiti...

653
01:06:35,000 --> 01:06:36,911
...bar ne za sada.

654
01:06:37,960 --> 01:06:40,190
A što se tice te devojke,

655
01:06:40,360 --> 01:06:43,875
Sutra bi mogla sa potraži
vojnicko odelo.

656
01:06:44,040 --> 01:06:46,190
Mogla bi mi uznemiriti
vojnike.

657
01:06:47,240 --> 01:06:50,357
A ti
cini mi se Rasputin...

658
01:06:51,240 --> 01:06:54,915
kako se zoveš?
- Rasputin, vaše Velišanstvo!

659
01:06:56,600 --> 01:06:58,670
Mora da si malo lud.

660
01:06:58,840 --> 01:07:00,831
Izvinite me, vaše Velicanstvo...

661
01:07:01,000 --> 01:07:03,150
...ali jedini ludak ovde
je Corto Maltese.

662
01:07:06,360 --> 01:07:09,557
Imao si srece.
- Kloni se ovoga, Mongolu!

663
01:07:09,720 --> 01:07:12,029
Ras, neverovatan si.

664
01:07:12,200 --> 01:07:15,158
Udjite unutra. Bar ce
vam biti toplo.

665
01:07:25,560 --> 01:07:27,790
"U Xanadu je Kubla Khan

666
01:07:27,960 --> 01:07:31,077
Mesto ispenjenim zadovoljstvom:

667
01:07:31,240 --> 01:07:33,470
Gde Alph, sveta reka, protice

668
01:07:33,640 --> 01:07:36,757
kroz pecine velicine coveka

669
01:07:36,920 --> 01:07:38,990
Sve do samoga mora.

670
01:07:39,160 --> 01:07:41,435
Dva puta vece od plodne zemlje

671
01:07:41,600 --> 01:07:43,875
Okovano zidovima
naokolo:

672
01:07:44,040 --> 01:07:46,759
U baštama umivanim
krivudavim potocicima,

673
01:07:46,920 --> 01:07:49,639
Gde mnogi blagosloveni behu
tamljanom;

674
01:07:49,800 --> 01:07:51,950
I šumama starim
koliko i samim planinama,

675
01:07:52,120 --> 01:07:54,998
ovejanim suncanim predelima."

676
01:07:55,240 --> 01:07:58,277
Sumnjam da ste hteli da pricate
o peziji samnom?

677
01:07:59,400 --> 01:08:00,833
Zašto ne?

678
01:08:01,000 --> 01:08:04,595
Pozija i mac cesto idu
zajedno.

679
01:08:06,040 --> 01:08:08,508
Poezija i veliki topovi...

680
01:08:09,400 --> 01:08:11,311
...nebaš tako cesto.

681
01:08:11,480 --> 01:08:12,879
Sedi molim te!

682
01:08:14,840 --> 01:08:16,990
Imam predlog za tebe.

683
01:08:17,880 --> 01:08:21,395
za tri da na moja divizija ce ici
da zauzme Ourga.

684
01:08:21,560 --> 01:08:25,155
Odatle cu da nastavim ka
Tchoibalsan-u i Sukhe Bator-u.

685
01:08:25,320 --> 01:08:27,072
Ništa neznam.

686
01:08:27,240 --> 01:08:29,231
Oni su subverzivni.

687
01:08:29,760 --> 01:08:32,194
Moram da zapocnem novi rat,

688
01:08:32,360 --> 01:08:34,749
kontrarevoluciju...

689
01:08:35,240 --> 01:08:37,515
...mnogo opasniju nego
 revoluciju.

690
01:08:38,200 --> 01:08:40,509
Vreme je vratiti se
našim starim verovanjima .

691
01:08:40,680 --> 01:08:44,355
Ratna etika i Šamanzam
ce biti naša nova religija.

692
01:08:46,600 --> 01:08:49,478
Od Japanske obale go Finskog zaliva,

693
01:08:49,640 --> 01:08:52,837
the yellow sun will fight the red star.

694
01:08:54,440 --> 01:08:56,271
Come with me.

695
01:08:59,000 --> 01:09:01,798
If I admit the need
to believe in something,

696
01:09:02,360 --> 01:09:05,079
then why should I choose Mongolia...

697
01:09:05,560 --> 01:09:07,630
...over a courtyard in Venice,

698
01:09:07,800 --> 01:09:09,916
the "Courtyard of Secrets"?

699
01:09:10,080 --> 01:09:13,311
Because no man is at peace with himself.

700
01:09:13,560 --> 01:09:16,677
I'm offering you a new empire!

701
01:09:16,920 --> 01:09:18,990
I have turned down so many things.

702
01:09:19,480 --> 01:09:21,789
This is first time someone has offered
me an empire.

703
01:09:22,920 --> 01:09:24,751
But I refuse.

704
01:09:24,920 --> 01:09:28,469
I don't force anyone to follow me,
Corto Maltese.

705
01:09:30,520 --> 01:09:32,795
"No" is such a beautiful word...

706
01:09:33,480 --> 01:09:36,119
...but only if you say it first,

707
01:09:36,280 --> 01:09:38,350
and you've had the courage.

708
01:09:39,560 --> 01:09:41,471
A toast to our future!

709
01:09:42,920 --> 01:09:45,309
Your Excellency, here's the Mopa.

710
01:09:47,800 --> 01:09:49,711
Homage to Buddha. In the language of the gods,
the Naga,

711
01:09:49,880 --> 01:09:51,791
the people and demons
I shall read the holy word.

712
01:09:51,960 --> 01:09:53,871
He's a Tibetan fortune-teller.

713
01:09:54,040 --> 01:09:56,838
He'll reveal the secrets of
life and death to us.

714
01:11:13,960 --> 01:11:15,712
The "Tree of Destiny"

715
01:11:15,880 --> 01:11:17,074
has millions of leaves

716
01:11:17,240 --> 01:11:19,879
and on each leaf the fate of
one person is written.

717
01:11:20,760 --> 01:11:24,196
Each time someone dies,
a leaf falls down.

718
01:11:25,560 --> 01:11:27,630
And I saw yours.

719
01:11:34,520 --> 01:11:36,511
There's a black dragon in your life.

720
01:11:36,680 --> 01:11:38,671
A twisting black dragon.

721
01:11:39,960 --> 01:11:42,599
But anyone who knows
to live like you, Corto,

722
01:11:42,760 --> 01:11:44,910
would even feel at ease in hell.

723
01:11:48,360 --> 01:11:50,828
And now, goodbye...

724
01:11:51,000 --> 01:11:53,958
Remember Corto, a twisting
black dragon.

725
01:11:59,480 --> 01:12:02,677
The Black Dragon? That's a Chinese
military sect...

726
01:12:02,920 --> 01:12:06,276
...however it also symbolises
the river Amur.

727
01:12:06,440 --> 01:12:08,670
Maybe he was suggesting
you should go there.

728
01:12:08,840 --> 01:12:10,751
To the Amur river?

729
01:12:10,920 --> 01:12:12,114
Too far away.

730
01:12:14,280 --> 01:12:16,840
Leave now... take your friends.

731
01:12:17,000 --> 01:12:18,911
Goodbye, Corto Maltese.

732
01:12:33,080 --> 01:12:35,071
That was a great adventure,
don't you agree?

733
01:12:35,240 --> 01:12:37,231
No I don't!

734
01:12:37,400 --> 01:12:40,119
That's not enough for me,
I want my share of the gold!

735
01:12:40,280 --> 01:12:43,875
If you want the gold, you'll have to dive
into the Three Border Lake yourself.

736
01:12:44,600 --> 01:12:47,558
Stop your childish behaviour,
it's no longer amusing!

737
01:12:47,720 --> 01:12:50,473
I don't understand why the baron
let us go.

738
01:12:51,080 --> 01:12:53,310
The shaman advised him.

739
01:12:53,720 --> 01:12:57,076
He also said I should watch out
for a twisting black dragon.

740
01:13:59,240 --> 01:14:01,549
Ever since his train was immobilised,

741
01:14:01,720 --> 01:14:03,950
his men are dying of hunger and cold

742
01:14:04,120 --> 01:14:06,509
and Kolchak's gold is yours, general.

743
01:14:06,680 --> 01:14:08,750
It's waiting for you...
in the Three Border Lake.

744
01:14:08,920 --> 01:14:10,831
It's not that simple.

745
01:14:11,400 --> 01:14:14,073
The Red Lanterns have
got a formidable ally now.

746
01:14:14,240 --> 01:14:15,912
That sailor, Corto Maltese?

747
01:14:16,120 --> 01:14:17,792
No, no...

748
01:14:17,960 --> 01:14:21,953
The Red Lanterns will dispose of him
now that the gold is where they want it..

749
01:14:22,120 --> 01:14:24,190
...in the Three Border Lake.

750
01:14:24,360 --> 01:14:26,669
The region is under control
of Sukhe Bator.

751
01:14:26,840 --> 01:14:28,831
He's their main ally.

752
01:14:29,000 --> 01:14:31,116
But general-baron Von Ungern is still around

753
01:14:31,280 --> 01:14:34,033
to fight Sukhe Bator.
- Could be...

754
01:14:34,360 --> 01:14:36,430
...but not at this moment...

755
01:14:37,000 --> 01:14:39,639
...and not for the gold.

756
01:14:41,160 --> 01:14:44,118
Yes, we'll have deal with Sukhe Bator.

757
01:15:11,400 --> 01:15:14,995
Sukhe Bator, my friend!
I'm Changaï-Li. Remember me?

758
01:15:15,160 --> 01:15:17,799
Yes, and I also remember you
had another name.

759
01:15:17,960 --> 01:15:20,394
But you probably had a good reason
to change it.

760
01:15:20,680 --> 01:15:22,352
Who's that Russian officer?

761
01:15:22,520 --> 01:15:25,956
He's neither an officer, nor Russian.
His name is Corto Maltese.

762
01:15:28,520 --> 01:15:30,351
Is he your husband?

763
01:15:31,800 --> 01:15:34,519
No... he's a loner.

764
01:15:36,080 --> 01:15:37,593
General Tchang's train!

765
01:15:38,920 --> 01:15:41,150
He's entering the valley!

766
01:15:45,000 --> 01:15:47,833
The warlord has never ventured
this far before.

767
01:15:48,000 --> 01:15:50,036
We must stop him.

768
01:16:00,760 --> 01:16:02,830
We'll soon arrive in Bolkang-Nor,
general.

769
01:16:03,000 --> 01:16:05,468
We'll stop for a few hours.
The soldiers are in need of some entertainment

770
01:16:05,640 --> 01:16:07,551
before we leave for Mongol.

771
01:16:07,720 --> 01:16:09,870
Let them visit the women.

772
01:16:10,520 --> 01:16:12,317
But be on the look-out for deserters.

773
01:17:03,160 --> 01:17:05,628
You there! Are you sure you're
in the right wagon?

774
01:17:05,800 --> 01:17:08,189
Are you talking to me?
- Yes, you.

775
01:17:08,360 --> 01:17:11,272
I've never seen you before.
- I haven't seen you before either.

776
01:17:22,120 --> 01:17:24,111
Corto...
- Yes?

777
01:17:24,440 --> 01:17:27,318
Do we have a reason for doing this?

778
01:17:28,280 --> 01:17:31,238
Any moral objections?
- No, I'm just asking.

779
01:17:31,400 --> 01:17:33,630
Listen... we've been friends long enough

780
01:17:33,800 --> 01:17:36,997
to ask you for help on this adventure.

781
01:17:37,160 --> 01:17:39,628
Anyhow, it was you who wanted an adventure!

782
01:17:55,800 --> 01:17:59,076
You can also shoot if you want!
- What?

783
01:17:59,240 --> 01:18:02,038
What do you really think of me?
Be honest!

784
01:18:02,200 --> 01:18:04,998
What do I think of you?
What's the catch?

785
01:18:05,160 --> 01:18:07,879
I just want to know.

786
01:18:08,840 --> 01:18:12,594
I'd love to have some friends,
but it never works out.

787
01:18:12,760 --> 01:18:14,591
Why is that?

788
01:18:14,760 --> 01:18:16,910
Am I not like everyone else?

789
01:18:17,240 --> 01:18:20,357
Of course you are... actually no...

790
01:18:20,520 --> 01:18:22,988
...maybe not... stop asking
all these questions!

791
01:18:23,160 --> 01:18:25,469
Now you're attacking me, while I'm
just explaining myself.

792
01:18:25,640 --> 01:18:27,358
I just want frie...

793
01:18:42,520 --> 01:18:46,069
General, mutiny among the artillerists!
They're firing at each other!

794
01:20:08,120 --> 01:20:11,874
Excellent work, comrade Changaï-Li!
We're proud of you!

795
01:20:14,760 --> 01:20:16,591
I'm sorry...

796
01:20:17,400 --> 01:20:20,358
...but we can't check
if they've survived.

797
01:20:20,520 --> 01:20:23,956
We have to get back to the Three Border Lake.
- I know.

798
01:20:24,120 --> 01:20:27,635
Are you crying?
- Me, crying?!

799
01:20:29,320 --> 01:20:31,311
You're mistaken!

800
01:20:31,880 --> 01:20:33,950
Besides, that's my business!

801
01:20:34,120 --> 01:20:36,509
You have a bad attitude, comrade.

802
01:20:37,160 --> 01:20:39,469
But that's your business too.

803
01:21:04,120 --> 01:21:06,998
At that moment I thought I'd never
see him again.

804
01:21:07,160 --> 01:21:09,549
Later I learned that Corto had survived...

805
01:21:09,720 --> 01:21:12,439
...he was one of the few survivors
of that disaster.

806
01:21:12,600 --> 01:21:15,160
You'd almost believe
a God is watching over sailors!

807
01:21:16,840 --> 01:21:19,957
They had taken him to a military hospital
in Kharbin...

808
01:21:21,720 --> 01:21:24,996
...together with one of his friends,
a certain Rasputin.

809
01:21:25,720 --> 01:21:27,472
Corto's eyes were hurt.

810
01:21:27,640 --> 01:21:29,471
A few days later he was doing better

811
01:21:29,640 --> 01:21:32,200
and I could help him leave
for Hong Kong.

812
01:21:32,840 --> 01:21:34,910
He absolutely wanted to go there.

813
01:21:36,600 --> 01:21:38,989
When we were talking about the duchess...

814
01:21:40,160 --> 01:21:42,993
...I got a feeling he was hiding
something.

815
01:21:49,640 --> 01:21:53,235
Corto Maltese arrived somewhere
during March.

816
01:21:53,400 --> 01:21:55,470
I was happy to see him again.

817
01:21:56,200 --> 01:21:58,111
It were rough times...

818
01:21:58,280 --> 01:22:01,636
...but apparently he was the only
one who didn't realise that.

819
01:22:01,960 --> 01:22:03,712
He knew...

820
01:22:03,880 --> 01:22:07,270
...Tchang had survived
and was hiding in Hong Kong.

821
01:22:07,640 --> 01:22:11,315
The Triad had decided to eliminate
the warlord.

822
01:22:11,480 --> 01:22:16,474
So we helped Corto to find him.

823
01:22:17,640 --> 01:22:21,633
It had become a personal affair for him.

824
01:22:23,560 --> 01:22:27,235
But I'll try to be more precise:

825
01:22:31,400 --> 01:22:33,391
A certain night...

826
01:22:55,080 --> 01:22:58,117
I heard from a friend in the Triad
that you were still alive.

827
01:23:01,000 --> 01:23:03,070
It was a nice adventure.

828
01:23:07,960 --> 01:23:09,791
What was that girl's name again?

829
01:23:11,320 --> 01:23:13,959
Changaï-Li.
- Changaï-Li?

830
01:23:14,840 --> 01:23:17,638
Sounds like the title of an American operetta.

831
01:23:20,680 --> 01:23:22,636
Yes, lieutenant?

832
01:23:23,480 --> 01:23:26,358
In name of His British Majesty
I arrest you.

833
01:23:26,520 --> 01:23:28,511
What am I accused of?

834
01:23:28,680 --> 01:23:33,310
Pillaging, armed mutiny,
murder, arms trade, treason.

835
01:23:35,640 --> 01:23:37,198
One Ear, you can bring the tea.

836
01:23:37,960 --> 01:23:40,030
Thank you, general, but there's
no time.

837
01:23:40,200 --> 01:23:42,998
Major Osborne and colonel Rand
are waiting for us.

838
01:23:48,840 --> 01:23:51,798
You're still in Hong Kong?
Didn't you leave?

839
01:23:51,960 --> 01:23:54,713
I left... and I came back.

840
01:24:10,760 --> 01:24:13,957
His tea was poisoned.
- The servant!

841
01:24:14,120 --> 01:24:16,350
He was just following his master's orders.

842
01:24:16,520 --> 01:24:18,829
Maybe, but it's still murder.

843
01:24:19,000 --> 01:24:22,436
One Ear, you'll need a good lawyer.
I'll take care of it.

844
01:24:22,600 --> 01:24:24,511
I thank you.

845
01:24:25,160 --> 01:24:27,230
I thought you were mute.

846
01:24:29,320 --> 01:24:32,517
There. That's all I can tell you.

847
01:24:32,920 --> 01:24:35,878
He left for the Kiang-Si region.

848
01:24:39,320 --> 01:24:41,151
What for...

849
01:24:41,320 --> 01:24:43,231
...I don't know.

850
01:26:25,880 --> 01:26:27,950
Who are those girls?

851
01:26:28,440 --> 01:26:30,510
Red Lantern apprentices?

852
01:26:30,680 --> 01:26:34,912
Yes, but currently they are taking
lessons at Kiang's new school.

853
01:26:35,320 --> 01:26:37,390
I'm their teacher.

854
01:26:44,440 --> 01:26:47,000
You want to know what happened to the gold?

855
01:26:49,200 --> 01:26:52,749
We were able to retrieve
from the Three Border Lake.

856
01:26:53,080 --> 01:26:56,117
It'll be used to build a large
hydroelectric plant.

857
01:26:56,440 --> 01:26:58,954
Asia and the weak Red Lanterns
thank you.

858
01:26:59,480 --> 01:27:01,710
The "weak" Red Lanterns?

859
01:27:16,280 --> 01:27:18,589
How's your friend Rasputin?

860
01:27:19,160 --> 01:27:21,390
He stayed with me for a week in Hong Kong

861
01:27:21,560 --> 01:27:24,279
and then disappeared with my Gauguin painting.

862
01:27:24,440 --> 01:27:27,876
But as compensation he did something
he'd never done before.

863
01:27:28,840 --> 01:27:30,910
He wrote me a letter!

864
01:27:33,480 --> 01:27:36,278
That's Ling over there, an agricultural engineer.

865
01:27:37,480 --> 01:27:39,471
Ling is my husband.

866
01:27:44,920 --> 01:27:47,992
I'm was curious to meet you, Mister Corto Maltese.

867
01:27:48,360 --> 01:27:50,271
Second Beauty has told me a lot about you.

868
01:27:50,440 --> 01:27:52,510
"Second Beauty" is my first name.

869
01:27:52,680 --> 01:27:55,399
I know you've met during
a revolutionary operation in Manchuria.

870
01:27:55,560 --> 01:27:58,279
She did great!

871
01:27:59,560 --> 01:28:01,790
But you were great too!

872
01:28:02,280 --> 01:28:05,033
Tonight the students and the farmers
would like to perform

873
01:28:05,200 --> 01:28:07,953
a theatre play in your honour.

874
01:28:12,920 --> 01:28:15,992
I'll leave you now. You probably
have a lot to talk about.

875
01:28:21,560 --> 01:28:24,279
Ling is a great husband.
I didn't want...

876
01:28:35,880 --> 01:28:37,393
Where are you going?

877
01:28:39,160 --> 01:28:40,593
I don't know.

878
01:28:44,360 --> 01:28:46,430
Goodbye, Changaï-Li.

879
01:29:37,000 --> 01:29:49,248
PREVOD I OBRADA
